
  N I C H U

Nichu is a basic quick image hosting solution in PHP inspired of
Imageshack. It was made to be as simple as possible to install and
to be usable even on low-cost shared hosting. While it has very few
features, Nichu is fast, secured, and easily customisable.

Requierments :
 * PHP4 or PHP5
 * The GD module


Installation
------------
 * Extract this archive on your serveur
 * Make sure that the 'img' and 'thumb' folders have writting
   permissions
 * (optionnal) modify config.php
 * Profit !!!


